# .deployignore — paths excluded from public publish at schemas.luh.tech/ectropy/*
# Enforced by luh-tech/schema-registry deploy-pages.yml (rsync --exclude-from).
# This repo currently contains only the classified-public allow-list (nothing to
# exclude today) - this file exists as defense-in-depth: if a non-public schema is
# ever added here by mistake, this is the first line of defense before the deploy
# workflow's own leak-guard (which hard-checks all 6 known proprietary schema names
# by path) catches it as a second, independent check.
#
# The 6 product-mechanism schemas live in the private luh-tech/schemas repo and
# should never be added here. If one ever needs to be added by mistake and then
# caught, add its path below AND file an incident - this list being non-empty is
# itself a signal something went wrong upstream.

# --- Never publish: repo internals / build artifacts ---
.git/
.github/
.deployignore
README.md
_site/
